The paper deals with image annotation and machine learning, which are both core topics in computer vision (cs.CV). The specific application domain is forensic imagery, which falls under computer security and cryptography (cs.CR). The paper also discusses transfer learning, which is a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper presents a method for improving annotation accuracy, which is a problem in machine learning (cs.LG).
